Class AntPlusGenericControllableDevicePcc.IpcDefines

java.lang.Object

Enclosing class:
AntPlusGenericControllableDevicePcc
public static class AntPlusGenericControllableDevicePcc.IpcDefines extends Object
Defines the keys and values used to communicate between the PCC and plugin. User code should never have to reference these defines.
